  `AffineScheme ‚âå CommRing·µí·µñ` given by `AffineScheme.Spec : CommRing·µí·µñ ‚•§ AffineScheme` and
  `AffineScheme.Œì : AffineScheme·µí·µñ ‚•§ CommRing`.
